                    </Paragraph>
                    <Paragraph Margin="0, 20, 5, 0">
                        <Bold>1. Q: I am confused, the Search Page filters keep giving me error messages. What do I do?</Bold>
                    </Paragraph>
                    <Paragraph Margin="0, 20, 5, 0">
                        1. A: Sometimes you may accidentally insert wrong kind of format to the field, please consult to Help Page for formatting information.
                    </Paragraph>
                    <Paragraph Margin="0, 20, 5, 0">
                        <Bold>2. Q: I am using the Chart Page to view graphs about Finnish Vehicles. I noticed some fields are active only sometimes. Why?</Bold>
                    </Paragraph>
                    <Paragraph Margin="0, 20, 5, 0">
                        2. A: Chart filters have different options available for each selection. Some selections do not allow filters for every row because they are not relevant to the filter and to avoid the program from breking in use.
                    </Paragraph>
                    <Paragraph Margin="0, 20, 5, 0">
                        <Bold>3. Q: Where can I view my previous search results?</Bold>
                    </Paragraph>
                    <Paragraph Margin="0, 20, 5, 0">
                        3. A: You can find your previous search result history acessing the Main Page from the navigation bar. Clicking them will show the result again.
                    </Paragraph>
